    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You realize that not every situation should be solved with a gun. You're an intellectual as well as a warrior, solving problems logically and learning about the galaxy. You keep your mind sharp with formal education or self-guided study. When logic breaks down, you're always ready to fall back on your combat training.</p><p>Choose either Diplomacy or Society. You become trained in the chosen skill and one Lore skill of your choice. When you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e-anachronism.class-features.Item.vt4e3FdwvI3hNkEf]{Armor Expertise}, you gain expert proficiency in Diplomacy or Society (whichever you selected) and the Lore skill you selected. This increases to master proficiency when you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e-anachronism.class-features.Item.Gs1MRPZ3s3TXwEsX]{Armor Mastery}, and to legendary proficiency when you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e-anachronism.class-features.Item.5uMdhwOXbamPbNHA]{Legendary Armor}. You also gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e-anachronism.actions.Item.TBLHu4RhvhPrKid6]{Oppressive Presence} action.</p>",
